### Lấy tất cả bookings
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/bookings
Content-Type: application/json

### Lấy booking theo ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/bookings
Content-Type: application/json

### Tạo booking mới
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/bookings
Content-Type: application/json

