### Cập nhật booking
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/v1/bookings
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "paymentStatus": "paid",
  "notes": "Khách đã thanh toán full"
}

### Xoá booking
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/v1/bookings
Content-Type: application/json
